title: Finland will seek to join NATO, leaders say, ditching decades of neutrality despite Russia's threats of retaliation - CNN
content:

description: Finland's government said Sunday it intends to join NATO, ditching decades of neutrality and ignoring Russian threats of possible retaliation as the Nordic country attempts to strengthen its security following the onset of the war in Ukraine. Sweden's ruling party later said it will also support joining the alliance.
